Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.55,0:00:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just supposed to be an ordinary third grader,\N but then a small incident happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.50,0:00:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I received was a courageous heart.\N What I gained were magical powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.85,0:00:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With our new encounter, our destinies\N have been set in motion once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're both traveling through a forest of bewilderment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I'm sure the small light illuminating\N our feelings lies within both our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.92,0:00:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to believe in that light and travel\N that path, even if it ends in the darkest skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha will now begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:01:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}I was always so uneasy that I was shaking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}Hugging my knees in the corner of my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.03,0:01:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}I was afraid of knowing the "truth"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.87,0:01:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}and closed the door to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}Through a kind lie, I discovered where I should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}I fled and took refuge in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.63,0:01:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}No one knows of the lonely sea
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.59,0:01:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}being dyed a deep blue color
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.97,0:01:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}that hides my loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}With wholehearted feelings, I wounded your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}The secret within your eyes makes me want to soak it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}I'll bring the truth behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.46,0:01:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}your smile with a warm love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}If I touch it, the warmth that seems so breakable will
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}break away from its past and overflow.\NBecause you're always by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}I will no longer be puzzled over the shadow of loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.37,0:02:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears the battle is underway at their location.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.45,0:02:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The core of the Lost Logia is rated A+.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.71,0:02:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their actions seem haphazard and insecure, and as you\N can see, they're using their special attacks erratically.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This emergency affects us on a dimensional level.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.19,0:02:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to collect it as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.57,0:02:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enforcer Chrono Hallaoun. Can you make it out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The transfer coordinates are already set.\N Given the command, I can go at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:03:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Chrono, I order you to go to the combat site,\N cease all hostilities, and retrieve the Lost Logia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to their explanation of\N the circumstances, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You be careful out there, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I'll be going now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a Really Big Crisis?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.51,0:04:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commencing combat here is too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a government official from the Time-Space\N Administration Bureau, Chrono Hallaoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll need a detailed explanation about this from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time-Space Administration Bureau?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Firstly, withdraw your weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you continue to fight here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate! We have to withdraw! Get away from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.55,0:05:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Don't fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to run for it, Fate! Hold on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Combat has ceased.\N One of the two combatants has escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.48,0:05:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we trace her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She concealed her escape route by transferring\N multiple times. It doesn't look like we can follow her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:06:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he ended their battle in time, and we\N also managed to secure a Lost Logia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think everything ended well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, it seems like we'll\N find out what really happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.53,0:06:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chrono, good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I let the other one get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and I'd like to hear their story, so I was wondering\N if you could bring those two to the Asura?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, I will return momentarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuuno-kun... Yuuno-kun, what is this place...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We seem to be inside the Time-Space Administration\N Bureau's Dimensional Cruise Patrol Warship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Umm... to put it simply, we're inside a ship that\N moves through space between dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I... I don't think that's really simplifying it much...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Umm, let's see... along with the world you live in...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...there are hundreds of others similar\N to it, including the world I come from.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This ship and the people of the Time-Space\N Administration Bureau travel between them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and supervise the affairs of those worlds when\N they interfere with dimensional space.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.02,0:07:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you must be uncomfortable in that outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can release your barrier jacket and device here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right. Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also... shouldn't you return to your true form, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes! Now that you mention it, I guess I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been in this form for so long\N that I'd completely forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's been a while since you've\N seen me in this form, huh, Nanoha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nanoha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.71,0:08:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuno-kun, you're... Y-Yuuno-kun, you're a...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, what the heck's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But w-weren't you just a... no way!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did your images of each other just change?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... N-Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we first met, I was in this form, wasn't I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no! Y-You were a ferret to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.41,0:08:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah! T-That's right, isn't it!\N Ah, sorry about that! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never did show you my true form.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.69,0:08:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You never did! You really surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... can I say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on between you two, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the captain is waiting, and we'd like to\N hear your story as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.54,0:09:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, this way please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, I've arrived with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, please come in. Make yourselves at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.07,0:09:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who excavated the\N Lost Logia... the Jewel Seeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... and I went there to retrieve them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at the same time, it was also reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.18,0:10:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... just what are the Lost Logia?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... if I told you they were relics of a lost world,\N you probably wouldn't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Within dimensional space, there exist countless worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless worlds that are all\N born and grow on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among them, there existed a world\N that was just too evolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.03,0:10:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because their technology and science was too\N advanced, they ended up destroying their own world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that remained were the dangerous\N technological relics of the lost world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The general term given to one of\N those relics is a "Lost Logia."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.03,0:10:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How they're supposed to be used is unknown,\N but depending on the user...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it can harness enough power to not only destroy\N a single world, but all of dimensional space.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:10:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an incredibly dangerous technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:11:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must handle those items properly, and they must\N be stored in a proper place for safekeeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.67,0:11:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Lost Logia you two are searching\N for... the Jewel Seeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are crystallized forms of energy\N for dimensional interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If several Seeds were activated together, a dimensional\N distortion would occur and, worst case scenario...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a dimensional dislocation could be created\N because they're so dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.92,0:11:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you fought that black mage, that flash of light\N was an explosion which had a huge impact on space.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a dimensional distortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even using a couple thousandths of its power\N can cause that large of a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The effect of gathering and activating several of them\N to their fullest extent at once is unfathomable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of that happening once before...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the year 462 going by our old lunar calendar,\N a dimensional dislocation occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:11:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That was a terrible incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many of its adjacent worlds were\N completely annihilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a horrible tragedy that\N will always stain our history.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let that happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'd like to inform you that the\N Time-Space Administration Bureau...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will take over all authority regarding\N the Lost Logia, the Jewel Seeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be best if you two just forgot\N about what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...returned to your separate worlds,\N and continued to live your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This incident involves dimensional interference!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.14,0:12:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a simple matter that we could\N let civilians get involved with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:12:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:13:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we brought this up so suddenly,\N so you probably can't think clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why don't you two think it over this evening\N and discuss it between yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.85,0:13:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can discuss everything again in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you back. Where we\N were before is okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, should we go home...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And umm... I guess you're about my age?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... yeah... probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... are you mad about this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really didn't mean for things to turn out this way, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it ended up looking like I was\N keeping it a secret from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... not at all. I was a little surprised, but that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... I'm sorry. And thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-For now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems more convenient for\N me to stay in this form, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go have dinner, and then do some thinking...\N about what to do from this point on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're amazing! Both of them are AAA class mages!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl in white seems like she'd be\N your type, Chrono. She's pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amy! I don't care about stuff like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at the average of this girl's\N magical power... it's 1.27 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the girl in black's is... 1.43 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they release their greatest\N powers, those numbers triple!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.22,0:14:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They exceed you in magical power\N statistics alone, huh, Chrono?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all there is to magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.84,0:14:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's also the ability to apply yourself\N to the situation at hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.86,0:14:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and sound judgement when faced\N with a problem, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.36,0:15:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust you. After all, you must be the most talented\N of us all here on the Asura, Chrono-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. You're looking at their data.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're amazing, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that much magical power flowed into a Lost Logia...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a dimensional distortion would undoubtedly occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those kids... we now know the reason why Nanoha-san\N and Yuuno-kun were gathering the Jewel Seeds, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I wonder why this girl in black\N was gathering them as well...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looked... pretty desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she has a strong reason\N for what she's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reason, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's such a young girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She still looks young enough to be\N relying on her mother's love...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if she's being raised like a normal girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.38,0:16:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the Time-Space Administration Bureau's\N shown up, we won't be able to continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run away... we'll go somewhere\N where we can be alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even though we managed to\N get away, he's a top class mage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he really tries to come after us, we might not be\N able to stay here forever without being noticed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that demon woman... your mother keeps\N saying all those things that make no sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's so cruel to you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't speak badly of Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will speak badly of her!\N Because I'm so worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever you're sad, my heart hurts so much\N it feels like it's being ripped to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever you're crying, my eyes and nose get all\N blurry and drippy, so much that I lose myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.73,0:17:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to be in pain or to cry anymore, Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's because you and me\N are linked in mind and spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... if you're ever hurting, I'll be sure to\N stop myself from being sad, to stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want you to smile and be happy, Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... why can't you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Arf...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you see... I want to grant my mother's wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not just for my mother.\N I'm sure... it's for myself, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... just a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only a little more until we reach the end,\N so will you give me your best until then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:17:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.88,0:18:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that you're not doing this because\N that woman's telling you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you're doing your best because\N it's for you, and you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll definitely always protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... Nanoha and I would like to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help us, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without me, I'm sure Nanoha's magical\N power will increase your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In collecting the Jewel Seeds, and\N fighting against that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or whichever way you choose,\N I'm pretty sure she'll really help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You sure have thought things over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I guess it'd be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mom- Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:19:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have them help us. I'd like to save our\N trump card until the last minute, if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Enforcer Chrono?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.11,0:19:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have two conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you must put yourselves in the hands of the\N Time-Space Administration Bureau for the time being...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to always follow our instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust that's all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nanoha, it's been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah... thanks, Yuuno-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Momoko, Nanoha...\N Kyouya and I are going out back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.64,0:19:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, will you be training again tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.94,0:19:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.01,0:19:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.69,0:19:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, so I'm not going to hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Wait, wait! Let me watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.41,0:19:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna come, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Just wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.61,0:20:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki, I see you're still the same as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... what was that important thing\N you wanted to talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.06,0:20:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I told my mom about what happened from the\N day I met Yuuno-kun all the way up to today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't really say the stuff about magic and\N Yuuno-kun's true form, but... I told her all that I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then I told her that because of everything,\N I had to leave the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that it might be dangerous, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see what I've begun with\N all my friends through to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.45,0:20:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:20:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be enough to make you worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:21:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... you know that I'll always worry about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'll be worried about you, Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were still thinking about which path to take...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I think I'd probably tell you that you can't\N do anything dangerous like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've already decided for yourself, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.99,0:21:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to finish what you've\N started with your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.61,0:21:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you still want to try talking things\N over with that other girl you met.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.11,0:21:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.23,0:21:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... have a nice trip, and don't\N regret anything you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.78,0:21:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring your father and brother around\N to my way of thinking, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.78,0:21:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... thank you, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.80,0:22:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can no longer turn back...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.81,0:22:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the path I've chosen...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.82,0:22:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is what I truly want to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.25,0:23:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry... hurry, Fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.34,0:23:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The promised land... Alhazred is awaiting us...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.36,0:23:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My... our utopia!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.00,0:23:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a little wish. I was stumbling
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.95,0:23:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and losing my way on my journey
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.62,0:23:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but since you were there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.39,0:23:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to keep smiling and stay happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.84,0:23:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the silver wind came looking for\N two who were lacking something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.64,0:24:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,beyond the cellophane sea and forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.34,0:24:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I was just crying in our city that's\N nothing more than a diorama.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.17,0:24:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for your warm hand
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.85,0:24:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you held out to me that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.62,0:24:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the ever-swaying years,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt you looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.99,0:24:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I had finally, finally found the secret key.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.32,0:24:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a little wish. Gather the lemon-colored
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.26,0:24:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drops of the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.90,0:24:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to gently light the path you're walking down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.79,0:24:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a little wish, even if it's a small one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.81,0:24:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say you can't do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.43,0:24:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then remember that because you were there,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.26,0:25:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to keep smiling and stay happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.11,0:25:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Yuuno-kun and I have ended up\N staying with the TSAB on their warship, the Asura!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.03,0:25:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}An incredible reaction of the Jewel\N Seeds, beyond anything we've ever seen before...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.33,0:25:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}And the reunion of\N Nanoha and Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.14,0:25:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Just what does\N Fate-chan's mother want...?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.67,0:25:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Next time on\N Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha:
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.46,0:25:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Episode Nine:\N The Decisive Battle Above the Ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.79,0:25:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Lyrical Magical won't lose!
